{"tid":1518193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府想重建大台","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:22:54.000Z","uid":81424,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd74ffa4290b0d77c66343bba7917f7457df88a","tid":1518193,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"政府拉晒Gphone, 油頭妹, 堡主<br />\n分分鐘就係想激起市民大眾對佢地嘅同情<br />\n畀佢地一個道德光環<br />\n跟住就由佢地代表香港人 同政府談判<br />\n<br />\n記住今次抗爭有聲有色係因為冇大台<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有大台 沒有代表<br />\n沒有談判 沒有出賣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算天琦出翻嚟<br />\n都唔可以畀佢代表我地同政府談判<br />\n何況係中箭同堡主?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee73134472597d07fac35c0ef219fc5aaddb1fb7","tid":1518193,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=712b3875\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=182b6dd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ef2b801c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"a2a6461a4f9edb1358960f6c3b969a9715fe21c5","tid":1518193,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=97bbbc7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654db09ae93625bb859782ef98566eaedad755e8","tid":1518193,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"擊碎政府陰謀<br />\n拒絕大台<br />\n另祝各位被捕義士早日獲釋"},{"pid":"41c8ea6e47cba2a4963cf8eadc7fe1d1da269282","tid":1518193,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80dae636031fd0b04d0c5100b610c623a0582a72","tid":1518193,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"bb8174f20881b4a8cf8a3d9959c864ec44603b47","tid":1518193,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a633ac6580eb080ec9ffb30d967afbb0953416cd","tid":1518